s=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀得呢d科通常都冇咩腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 佢地on9姐 關讀呢科咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情係佢地本身間學校問題添啦，教到班學生錯左科仲可以坐低應考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc0cbabc447efaf939b31e2bc1abcf6a5b6fdf","tid":185393,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見到fb有人真係大大聲話「有幾多人會對準考證？」/「學生信住學校」/「學生臨考壓力好大」<br />\n<br />\n我以前讀會考，收到準考證首先一定要對英文係報左Syllabus A定B，每一科係考中文定英文（我讀中文班但係數學同a.maths係考英文卷）<br />\n<br />\nAL嗰陣就要對主科係AL定AS<br />\n好重要一定要對<br />\n<br />\n係我要求高定咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要求高姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學校講咩就曬咩架啦，唔通會老點你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊時不論ce定al,學校都有提我地對<br />\n我自己都有對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042853e5162e440eacbe107763d6be2ac4274bff","tid":185393,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"正路啲學生應該都會知卷二係設計卷 當年個老師都千叮萬囑叫我地小心睇清楚有冇報錯<br />\n不過真係慘嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩份卷兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0edbac25c964ff6a85e034bf81798625d20a0f","tid":185393,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:25:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩低嗰17個錯科都照考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀得呢d科通常都冇咩腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 佢地on9姐 關讀呢科咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情係佢地本身間學校問題添啦，教到班學生錯左科仲可以坐低應考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點考，d野應該完全冇學過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ae9398e75fca5995c6c66748485fc77df0a198","tid":185393,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見到fb有人真係大大聲話「有幾多人會對準考證？」/「學生信住學校」/「學生臨考壓力好大」<br />\n<br />\n我以前讀會考，收到準考證首先一定要對英文係報左Syllabus A定B，每一科係考中文定英文（我讀中文班但係數學同a.maths係考英文卷）<br />\n<br />\nAL嗰陣就要對主科係AL定AS<br />\n好重要一定要對<br />\n<br />\n係我要求高定咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAS考少AL半日。<br />\n學校應該就有出錯咖喇⋯一個學生就話啫⋯二十個喎依家⋯信人為錯好過信電腦錯⋯<br />\n不過學生都唔係完全冇責任。"},{"pid":"4cd288c87728b2b81e6dd67e06ac8f9d0fe943be","tid":185393,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"總結：on9學校出on9學生"},{"pid":"7ae91d813de305611d27899b14d1b7485fb68df2","tid":185393,"uid":74085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:49:05.000Z","msg":"好慘其實，但照坐底考真係傻左d"},{"pid":"deecf3fefb22c6acd89c3242050249cfab224230","tid":185393,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"有咩理由唔同準考證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派個陣呀sir千叮萬囑一定要對一次所有野，因為有啲科嘅卷都有分中英文"},{"pid":"c97d2811cb930b81605b84f662e05fb639083e3e","tid":185393,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩理由唔<span style=\"color: red;\">對</span>準考證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派個陣呀sir千叮萬囑一定要對一次所有野，因為有啲科嘅卷都有分中英文</blockquote>"},{"pid":"44aee62612105aca9b3601b38f48c9eb71e4b994","tid":185393,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:27:13.000Z","msg":"比我係個17個都照考啦<br />\n一試定生死點會唔考 何況係繪畫"},{"pid":"7afe8092f25d2fe932e231680435eaa01effc0a7","tid":185393,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:59:33.000